text: Very nice Pig organ soup with super Yummy yam rice !  Superb combo!  Home made garlic bits took the soup to another level !  Highly recommended !
The food here is actually really good. Pig organ soup is flavourful and yam rice has a lot of liao, like shrimp, yam, mushrooms, cabbage. Worth to eat!
